    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-8046-b6d8-e79bd490490e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "On a second experiment, authors use affect and disengaged behavior on the tutoring system to predict performance. Model achieves good correlation with standardized exam scores. ",
